{"word":"ἐκχωρέω","slug":"ἐκχωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκχωρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to go out and away, depart, emigrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to slip out of</i>, <el>ἐξεχώρησεν ἐξ ἄρθρων</el> <i>was dislocated</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to give way</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}